  "text": "The compilation scheme shown in the 'Original' column of Tab. 3 is what we believe to be a faithful representation of the original proposed scheme [CITATION_1] , informed by a series of interviews with the broader set of RSP designers. As a result of our formalisation work, we have found problems with this scheme, which we elucidate in §5.5. We propose instead the compilation scheme shown in the 'Proposed' column of Tab. 3, which addresses these problems. We now explain and justify our proposed scheme; a proof that it is sound follows in §6.",
